msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/date"
msgid "January 13th, 1945 · Thirimont, Ardennes, Belgium"
msgstr "13 de enero, 1945 - Thirimont, Ardenas, Bélgica"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/doctrine_allround"
msgid "Doctrine: All-Round"
msgstr "Doctrina: Completa"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/doctrine_defensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Defensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Defensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/doctrine_irregular"
msgid "Doctrine: Irregular"
msgstr "Doctrina: Irregular"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/doctrine_offensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Offensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/name"
msgid "The Bloody Ardennes"
msgstr "Las Ardenas sangrientas"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/name_big"
msgid "The Bloody Ardennes"
msgstr "Las Ardenas sangrientas"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Attention Fallschirmjäger! There is no time to lose! The Americans have "
"retaken the initiative and are now on the assault!"
msgstr ""
"¡Atención Fallschirmjäger! ¡No hay tiempo que perder! ¡Los americanos han "
"retomado la iniciativa y han lanzado un asalto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"You are tasked with defending our main line, here in the valley of "
"Thirimont. We will try to pin the Americans down, laying intense crossfire "
"as they hopefully get stuck in the snow. You have several AT guns at your "
"disposal."
msgstr ""
"Tienes la tarea de defender nuestra línea principal, aquí en el valle de "
"Thirimont. Intentaremos inmovilizar a los americanos, lanzando un intenso "
"fuego cruzado que esperamos que los deje atrapados en la nieve. Tienes "
"varios cañones AT a tu disposición."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"The Americans will be here any minute now. Deploy your squads around the "
"emplacements. There is no time to lose!"
msgstr ""
"Los americanos llegarán en cualquier momento. Desplieguen sus escuadrones "
"alrededor de las empalizadas. ¡No hay tiempo que perder!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"Enemy artillery just opened fire. Position your men on the camouflaged "
"foxholes and trenches that were prepared. We don't expect the americans to "
"hit those."
msgstr ""
"La artillería enemiga acaba de abrir fuego. Posicionen a sus hombres en las "
"trincheras camufladas que preparamos. Esperemos que los americanos no los "
"alcancen allí."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/05"
msgid "What the hell is that! We're getting bombed by airburst artillery!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué demonios es eso! ¡Nos están bombardeando con artillería antiaérea!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/06"
msgid ""
"Here they come! Let us spoil some new year's resolutions! Hold the line!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya están aquí! ¡Arruinemos algunos propósitos de año nuevo! ¡Mantengan la "
"posición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/07"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"Well done Fallschirmjäger. Our choice of position and our tactics have "
"decimated the Americans."
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho Fallschirmjäger. Nuestra posición y tácticas han diezmado a los "
"americanos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/09"
msgid ""
"Fallschirmjäger! The Americans have slipped through the defences of our "
"neighboring sector! They've swiftly snatched Thirimont from under our noses!"
msgstr ""
"¡Fallschirmjäger! ¡Los americanos han atravesado las defensas del sector "
"vecino! ¡Nos han arrebatado Thirimont delante de nuestras narices!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"I order you to take back the town and bust any of our troops out of "
"captivity immediately! "
msgstr ""
"¡Te ordeno que recuperes la ciudad y saques a cualquiera de nuestras tropas "
"cautivas inmediatamente! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"Repair as many American vehicles as possible to help us in the assault! Use "
"mortars and AT guns to provide support fire."
msgstr ""
"¡Repara tantos vehículos americanos como sea posible para ayudarnos en el "
"asalto! Utiliza morteros y cañones AT para proporcionar fuego de apoyo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Good job, Kameraden! But stop celebrating, we're not done yet. The Americans "
"are storing the captured weapons in the boxes on the stables."
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo, Kameraden! Pero dejad de celebrarlo, aún no hemos terminado. "
"Los americanos están almacenando las armas obtenidas en las cajas de los "
"establos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"Now, gentlemen! We mustn't let Thirimont fall once again to the Americans, "
"but it's clear our flanks are vulnerable. The only way to ensure success is "
"to defend the town itself."
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora, caballeros! No debemos dejar que Thirimont caiga una vez más en "
"manos de los americanos, pero está claro que nuestros flancos son "
"vulnerables. La única forma de asegurar el éxito es defender la ciudad."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/14"
msgid ""
"Fall back and get all of our emplacements to the town; be ready to defend "
"it! Loot all the boxes and supplies, find mines and obstacles. Make "
"Thirimont our unbreakable fortress!"
msgstr ""
"Retrocede y lleva todas las empalizadas a la ciudad; ¡prepárate para "
"defenderla! Saquea todas las cajas y suministros, encuentra minas y "
"barricadas. ¡Convierte Thirimont en una fortaleza inquebrantable!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/15"
msgid ""
"I've ordered our neighboring units in to defend Thirimont with us. Take "
"command of these men!"
msgstr ""
"He ordenado a las tropas vecinas que defiendan Thirimont con nosotros. "
"¡Tomen el mando de estos hombres!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/16"
msgid ""
"The enemy has started an intense artillery bombardment on the southern part "
"of town! I expect their attack to come from there!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo ha comenzado un intenso bombardeo de artillería en la parte sur "
"de la ciudad! ¡Creo que nos atacarán por allí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/17"
msgid ""
"The enemy is throwing heavier armor at us! Watch out for those sluggers. "
"They can take out our heaviest of tanks at a distance!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo está avanzando con blindados pesados hacia nosotros! Cuidado con "
"esos sluggers. ¡Pueden derribar hasta nuestros tanques más pesados a "
"distancia!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/18"
msgid ""
"Excellent job! Once again you have proven the might of the Fallschirmjäger "
"forces. If only all of our foces would have fought as gallantly as you have, "
"our winter offensive would have reached Antwerp!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! Una vez más han demostrado el poder de las fuerzas "
"Fallschirmjäger. Si todas nuestras fuerzas hubieran luchado con tanta "
"valentía como vosotros, ¡nuestra ofensiva de invierno habría llegado hasta "
"Amberes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/19"
msgid ""
"Well, those were the main scouting forces. I wonder what the Americans will "
"serve us up with next."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, esas eran las principales fuerzas de exploración. Me pregunto con qué "
"aparecerán ahora los americanos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/artywarning"
msgid ""
"The Americans like to shoot the hell out of everything, and anything that "
"looks even slightly suspicious. Do not set up positions in the open, deploy "
"your men around the camouflaged emplacements the engineers dugout during the "
"night."
msgstr ""
"A los estadounidenses les gusta disparar a todos lados y a todo lo que "
"parezca mínimamente sospechoso. No establezcas posiciones en campo abierto, "
"despliega a tus hombres alrededor de las empalizadas camufladas que los "
"ingenieros excavaron anoche."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/calliope"
msgid ""
"Achtung! The Americans have brought Calliope rocket launchers! Keep your "
"heads down!"
msgstr ""
"¡Atención! ¡Los americanos han traído lanzacohetes Calliope! ¡Agachaos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/normalarty"
msgid ""
"Well, that wasn't so bad! They actually improved our line of fire! Stupid "
"Americans!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ¡eso no fue tan mal! ¡En realidad mejoraron nuestra línea de fuego! "
"¡Estúpidos americanos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/narrator/reinf1"
msgid ""
"Some of our friendly forces from the collapsing flanks have arrived. I place "
"them under your command! Take Thirimont, Herr Leutnant!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestras fuerzas amigas de los flancos colapsados han llegado. ¡Las pongo "
"bajo su mando! ¡Tome Thirimont, Herr Leutnant!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"That was very well executed! You have shown the enemy our definition of "
"resilience and grit, and in doing so, you have made your unit look almost "
"invincible. The enemy will probably not try again very soon. Good job!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ha estado muy bien ejecutado! Has mostrado al enemigo nuestra definición de "
"resistencia y agallas, y al hacerlo, has hecho que tu unidad parezca casi "
"invencible. El enemigo no volverá a intentarlo por ahora. ¡Buen trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That did not go as planned, not at all. We have suffered losses we can’t "
"replace, how are we to recover from this blow? You will have to find an "
"explanation for this very quickly."
msgstr ""
"Esto no salió como estaba previsto, en absoluto. Hemos sufrido pérdidas "
"irremplazables, ¿cómo vamos a recuperarnos de este golpe? Tendrás que "
"encontrar rápidamente una solución para esto."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/place"
msgid "3rd Fallschirmjäger Division"
msgstr "3ª División Fallschirmjäger"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/skip"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Saltar la fase de preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/story"
msgid " It is now 1945. The Ardennes offensive is grinding to a halt. The Germans are still very badly hampered by fuel shortages; all along the front line, allied forces have taken the initiative. The weather has improved too, so the allied air forces once more rule the sky above the Ardennes. It looks like things have taken a turn for the worse for you and the 3rd Fallschirmjäger division as well.\n\n You are now in Thirimont, where the Americans are expected to attack soon. It will be your mission to stop them. You and your men have been sent forward from the 3rd Fallschirmjäger Division reserve as replacements for the losses which the 9th Regiment has suffered. The 9th regiment has orders to hold the line at Thirimont itself, which dominates the area. You are to defend this position and where possible, support the defenders on the neighboring hill when the Americans attack. We might be able to get you armored support at some point, but right now a handful of AT guns is all we can spare. So, prepare to defend the village, and await further orders.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"Estamos en 1945.\n"
"\n"
"La ofensiva de las Ardenas se está deteniendo.\n"
"\n"
"Los alemanes siguen muy perjudicados por la\n"
"\n"
"escasez de combustible; a lo largo de la línea del frente, las fuerzas "
"aliadas han\n"
"\n"
"han tomado la iniciativa. El tiempo también ha mejorado,\n"
"\n"
"por lo que las fuerzas aéreas aliadas una vez más dominan el cielo sobre\n"
"\n"
"Ardenas. Parece que las cosas han dado un giro\n"
"\n"
"para peor para ti y para la 3 ª división Fallschirmjäger.\n"
"\n"
"Ahora están en Thirimont, donde se espera que los americanos\n"
"\n"
"ataquen pronto.\n"
"\n"
"Tu misión será detenerlos.\n"
"\n"
"Usted y sus hombres han sido enviados al frente de la\n"
"\n"
"3 ª Fallschirmjäger División de reserva como sustitutos de las\n"
"\n"
"pérdidas que ha sufrido el 9º Regimiento.\n"
"\n"
"El 9º Regimiento tiene órdenes de mantener la posición en\n"
"\n"
"Thirimont, que domina la zona.\n"
"\n"
"Deben defender esta posición y donde sea posible,\n"
"\n"
"apoyar a los defensores en la colina vecina\n"
"\n"
"cuando los americanos ataquen.\n"
"\n"
"Podríamos conseguirles apoyo blindado en algún momento,\n"
"\n"
"pero en este momento un puñado de armas AT es todo lo que podemos utilizar.\n"
"\n"
"Así que prepárense para defender la aldea y esperen órdenes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/task1"
msgid "Hold the defensive line at the valley."
msgstr "Mantener la línea defensiva en el valle."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/task2"
msgid "Recapture the village of Thirimont and liberate the prisoners."
msgstr "Recapturar el pueblo de Thirimont y liberar a los prisioneros."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/task3"
msgid "Create a new defensive line around Thirimont"
msgstr "Crear una nueva línea defensiva alrededor de Thirimont"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/task4"
msgid "Do not let the village of Thirimont fall to the Americans again."
msgstr ""
"No dejes que el pueblo de Thirimont caiga de nuevo en manos de los "
"americanos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/timer1"
msgid "Time until the arrival of US forces:"
msgstr "Tiempo hasta la llegada de las fuerzas americanas:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/timer2"
msgid "Fortify the town of Thirimont:"
msgstr "Fortificar la ciudad de Thirimont:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1945_01_thirimont/timer3"
msgid "Defend the town of Thirimont!"
msgstr "¡Defiendan la ciudad de Thirimont!"
